    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s reliable, looks great, and is totally ready for the road? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend trip, this beauty won't let you down. Come by, say hi, and take it for a test drive\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I do!",
