    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal power delivery across the rear axle. Recent service includes a VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment, maintaining the high-revving integrity of the powerplant. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping for a communicative, analog road feel. A mechanically robust example ready for the apex.",
