    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Executive Sport Sedan offers a refined driving experience and a sophisticated aesthetic. Meticulously maintained, the vehicle features a robust turbocharged engine that provides smooth acceleration and impressive fuel efficiency. The exterior, finished in a deep Obsidian Black, retains a high-gloss shine, though closer inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper typical of highway driving. Inside, the charcoal leather interior is in great shape, featuring heated power seats, a premium 10-speaker sound system, and a panoramic sunroof that opens up the cabin. All electronics are fully functional, and the climate control remains ice-cold. Mechanically, the car is sound with a complete service history; the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently replaced. While there is slight wear on the steering wheel leather, the cabin remains quiet and rattle-free. This is a dependable, stylish vehicle perfect for a professional seeking comfort and performance.",
